Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮有什麼計劃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:53.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是出去購物之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:56.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長基本還是要打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:16:00.64,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord5\fs80\b1\pos(1339,946.6)}白銀御行想出遊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:59.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 比想像中更難調整出勤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,空閒時間還挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想幹點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想幹點什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 藤原書記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.08,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 藤原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:12.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,恐山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然討論過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是被保留了的旅行問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:25.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是腰斬還是實行全都由這個瞬間決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:28.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假種類繁多的活動中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:34.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是否男女混合舉行與起跑衝刺緊密相連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:37.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,男女最初一起出去都是「接下來去哪裡」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「那大家一起去吧」這樣發展的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:43.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 如果起跑衝刺失敗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就會增加男女混合的心理難度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,男生和男生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,女生和女生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:51.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣分組度過暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣失敗的話就是灰色的暑假生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:17:03.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 沒有沒有……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}不會背木屐帶斷了的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}試膽大會也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}不會回到老家和青梅竹馬再會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}穿越時間也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}異世界的召喚也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}不可能有夏日大冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}天體觀測時看見流星許願也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}暑假一起做作業也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}男女混合旅行也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:03.75,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord10\blur5}也不可能有被煙火聲遮蓋的情話
