Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:18.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那當天19點去那裡集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:19.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯我很期待
